From 0000000000000000000000000000000000000000 Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Samuel Attard <sattard@anthropic.com>
Date: Mon, 18 May 2026 10:52:13 +0100
Subject: feat: deliver service worker preload data via
 EmbeddedWorkerStartParams

Adds an opaque BigBuffer field to EmbeddedWorkerStartParams plus a
ContentBrowserClient::GetServiceWorkerStartupData() hook to populate it.
The blob rides the existing browser->renderer-main->worker-thread
marshalling that StartWorker already performs (GlobalScopeCreationParams
moved across the thread boundary by WorkerThread::Start), so embedder
service-worker startup data arrives on the worker thread ordered with
worker creation, with no renderer-side cross-thread global, lock, or
blocking wait. Exposed to the embedder on the worker thread via a new
WebServiceWorkerContextProxy::ElectronPreloadData() getter backed by
WorkerGlobalScope.

